title: Couple With Heart Woman Person Medium Light Skin Tone Light Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Couple With Heart (Person, Man, Medium-Light Skin Tone, Light Skin Tone)
description: Represents a romantic couple, specifically a person and a man, with their skin tones indicated as medium-light and light. Often used to express love, relationships, and partnerships.
apple_vendor_description: This heartwarming emoji on Apple devices depicts two figures, a woman and another person, tenderly connected with a stylized red heart floating between them, rendered in warm medium-light and light skin tones. Apple's signature smooth gradients and gentle 3D shading imbue the figures with a soft, affectionate glow, symbolizing love, partnership, and deep emotional connection in a universally understood way.
